hopobject.body: Very Good Site ciprofloxacin eye/ear drops side effects One of the two bombings in the town of Rafah brought down a two-story building housing the local branch of military intelligence. It collapsed the entire structure, two security officials said, speaking anonymously because they were not authorized to talk to the media. They said no bodies were found under the rubble, but the attack left 10 soldiers and seven civilians, three of them women, wounded.
